text: U pěti veverek is a 1944 Czechoslovak comedy film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Jaromíra Pacová, Jindřich Plachta, and Růžena Nasková. ==References== ==External links== *U pěti veverek at the Internet Movie Database Category:1944 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak comedy films Category:1944 comedy films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak black-and-white films
